(secondQuint)Paclitaxel in Combination With Carboplatin Versus Paclitaxel Plus Epirubicin in Metastatic Breast Cancer.

 A Randomized Prospective Clinical Trial of Paclitaxel in Combination with Carboplatin Versus Paclitaxel plus Epirubicin as First-Line Treatment in Metastatic Breast Cancer.

 The primary endpoints of the study is progression free survival (PFS).

 The secondary endpoints are overall response rate (ORR), overall survival (OS) and safety.

