Paclitaxel plus Epirubicin in metastatic breast cancer is a recommended scheme in National Comprehensive Cancer Network (NCCN) guideline.

 Paclitaxel in Combination with Carboplatin is also effective in Metastatic Breast Cancer (MBC) in some clinical study with small sample.

